659
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,980
 ali onda ostavljaš Ehov.

660
00:34:45,980 --> 00:34:49,280
 Nisam tako mislio,

661
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:49,840
 ja sam mislio,

662
00:34:49,840 --> 00:34:50,620
 kao, ma nema šanse,

663
00:34:50,620 --> 00:34:52,020
 ne možeš ići na dvije fronte,

664
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:52,820
 ne, ne možeš to,

665
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:53,880
 bireš šta hoćeš.

666
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:54,880
 Kao, i pita me,

667
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,140
 Marko, još si se pomolio?

668
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:58,920
 Rekao, pa jesam?

669
00:34:58,920 --> 00:34:59,680
 Kao, pa dobro,

670
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:00,380
 šta ti je Bog rekao?

671
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:03,360
 Pa rekao mi je i sad.

672
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:04,660
 Šta mi je Bog rekao?

673
00:35:04,660 --> 00:35:06,360
 Bog mi rekao tada,

674
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:07,560
 podsjetio me na jedan citat

675
00:35:07,560 --> 00:35:09,060
 koji godinama nisam pročitao.

676
00:35:09,060 --> 00:35:12,060
 Već sam ga spomenuo nekad ovdje,

677
00:35:12,060 --> 00:35:13,960
 kada je Natan rekao Davidu,

678
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:15,580
 kada je sagriješio sa Bat Šebom,

679
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:17,060
 kada mu je rekao,

680
00:35:17,060 --> 00:35:19,460
 sve sam ti dao.

681
00:35:19,460 --> 00:35:20,620
 Kaže Bog Davidu,

682
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:21,500
 sve sam ti dao.

683
00:35:21,500 --> 00:35:23,860
 I da ti je to bilo malo

684
00:35:23,860 --> 00:35:26,040
 i da si me tražio još,

685
00:35:26,040 --> 00:35:27,540
 ja bi ti dao još.

686
00:35:27,540 --> 00:35:29,600
 I kad sam to izgovaro,

687
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,040
 Mirjani,

688
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:31,280
 šta mi je rekao?

689
00:35:32,220 --> 00:35:33,080
 Knedla u grlu,

690
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:34,060
 ja u suzama,

691
00:35:34,060 --> 00:35:35,400
 kao,

692
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:36,240
 sve mi je jasno.

693
00:35:36,240 --> 00:35:37,420
 I znate šta se dogodilo?

694
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:38,620
 Nakon toga,

695
00:35:38,620 --> 00:35:39,320
 ja sam rekao,

696
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,020
 okej,

697
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:40,840
 jasno mi je.

698
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,540
 Neću filozofirati,

699
00:35:42,540 --> 00:35:43,780
 neću izmišljati o toplu vodu.

700
00:35:43,780 --> 00:35:44,760
 Bože,

701
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:45,740
 malo mi je,

702
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:46,560
 želim još.

703
00:35:46,560 --> 00:35:51,000
 Mjesec dana nakon toga,

704
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:52,860
 pokreću se stvari,

705
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:54,420
 pokreću se nove stvari,

706
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:55,880
 počinje se zavrtiti

707
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,260
 jedna nova priča,

708
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:58,460
 za tri mjeseca,

709
00:35:58,460 --> 00:35:59,520
 nitko ne vjeruje

710
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:00,800
 zašto se to tako dogodilo,

711
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:01,880
 šta se trebno događa,

712
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:02,440
 ni ja sam.

713
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:05,140
 I nedavno razgovaram

714
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:05,760
 s tom osobom

715
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,100
 i skužim,

716
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:07,120
 sve je krenulo

717
00:36:07,120 --> 00:36:08,920
 nakon onog trenutka

718
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,080
 i kad sam ja rekao njemu,

719
00:36:10,080 --> 00:36:10,760
 pa znaš šta,

720
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:12,020
 malo mi je,

721
00:36:12,020 --> 00:36:12,940
 želim više Bože.

722
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:15,380
 Bog je vjeran.

723
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:17,440
 Bog je vjeran.

724
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:19,640
 Samo,

725
00:36:19,640 --> 00:36:20,260
 jesi li ti?

726
00:36:20,260 --> 00:36:23,040
 Jesam li ja?

727
00:36:23,040 --> 00:36:25,820
 On će svoj dio odraditi.

728
00:36:25,820 --> 00:36:28,480
 Odrađujem li ja svoj dio?

729
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:31,900
 ili je sve moje

730
00:36:31,900 --> 00:36:32,960
 usmjereno na to

731
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,520
 samo da meni pomogne

732
00:36:34,520 --> 00:36:36,400
 da riješi moju situaciju,

733
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,720
 a Bože za tvoje,

734
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:38,880
 ako stignem?

735
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:41,360
 Ako stignem?

736
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:47,120
 Tko neki lik mi se nedavno javi,

737
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:47,460
 kaže,

738
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:49,400
 kroz cijelu Bibliju piše

739
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,400
 da je najvažnija stvar

740
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:51,440
 da imamo obitelj

741
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,560
 i djecu.

742
00:36:52,560 --> 00:36:53,640
 I rekao,

743
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,100
 ja ne znam

744
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:55,240
 koju Bibliju si čitao,

745
00:36:55,240 --> 00:36:55,520
 ali,

746
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:56,280
 volim te mi,

747
00:36:56,280 --> 00:36:57,900
 nađi hrpu citata

748
00:36:57,900 --> 00:36:59,100
 gdje je to najvažnija stvar.

749
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,200
 Najvažnija stvar,

750
00:37:00,200 --> 00:37:01,360
 da opoznamo Krista

751
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:02,800
 i onoga koga je on poslao.

752
00:37:03,120 --> 00:37:03,840
 To je da poveznamo

753
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,460
 Boga Otca

754
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:06,060
 i onoga koga je on poslao

755
00:37:06,060 --> 00:37:06,680
 Isusa Hrista.

756
00:37:06,680 --> 00:37:07,820
 To je najvažnija stvar

757
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:08,500
 za naš život.

758
00:37:08,500 --> 00:37:13,820
 I učinite sve druge

759
00:37:13,820 --> 00:37:14,960
 mojim učenicima.

760
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:19,480
 Ja se ne sjećam

761
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:20,800
 ni jedne zapovjede Isusove

762
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:22,460
 i ženite se,

763
00:37:22,460 --> 00:37:23,180
 imajte djecu

764
00:37:23,180 --> 00:37:24,940
 i zbrinite se

765
00:37:24,940 --> 00:37:25,720
 za svoju obitelj

766
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:27,100
 i učekaj sve ostalo.

767
00:37:27,100 --> 00:37:28,120
 To je najvažnija stvar.

768
00:37:28,120 --> 00:37:29,880
 Ne, ja nisam protiv toga.

769
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,940
 Pa će da, imaj obitelj.

770
00:37:31,940 --> 00:37:33,200
 Radi, crkvo malo.

771
00:37:33,200 --> 00:37:34,620
 Imaš prosor,

772
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:36,120
 tu odgadi, tako dalje.

773
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,480
 Ali ako ćemo pričati

774
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,180
 o poslanju,

775
00:37:38,180 --> 00:37:39,180
 šta je Bože volja?

776
00:37:39,180 --> 00:37:40,440
 Pa pročitajte.

777
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:42,680
 Šta je rekao?

778
00:37:42,680 --> 00:37:45,520
 Tražite najprije Bože kraljevstvo

779
00:37:45,520 --> 00:37:47,000
 i sve ostalo će vam se nadodati.

780
00:37:47,000 --> 00:37:49,880
 Pa ništa mi se ne nadodaje.

781
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:52,240
 Pa ne tražiš

782
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:53,580
 najprije Bože kraljevstvo.

783
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:59,580
 Ide u obrnutom smjeru.

784
00:38:00,340 --> 00:38:01,860
 Sad sam se naljutio.

785
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:05,660
 Sad, zašto imamo prepreku

786
00:38:05,660 --> 00:38:06,860
 razumiju tu Božju volju?

787
00:38:06,860 --> 00:38:10,340
 Prvo, imamo previše izbora.

788
00:38:10,340 --> 00:38:12,840
 Imamo previše izbora.

789
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:16,680
 Mi u bilo kojem trenutku

790
00:38:16,680 --> 00:38:18,180
 možemo doći do bilo čega

791
00:38:18,180 --> 00:38:19,980
 i previše nam je

792
00:38:19,980 --> 00:38:22,060
 i ne znamo šta da izaberemo.

793
00:38:23,700 --> 00:38:24,940
 Ko kad još u dovedem

794
00:38:24,940 --> 00:38:27,080
 u Millerika treba izabrati

795
00:38:27,080 --> 00:38:27,760
 i kad mu kažem

796
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:29,240
 budžet koji ima za igračku

797
00:38:29,240 --> 00:38:30,400
 i sad mu moram pokazati

798
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,440
 sve igračke

799
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:33,540
 koje može u tom budžetu izabrati

800
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:34,860
 i onda sve jedno,

801
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:35,980
 još i pola sata

802
00:38:35,980 --> 00:38:36,520
 moramo tamo

803
00:38:36,520 --> 00:38:38,040
 dok on izabere koju.

804
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:38,380
 Zašto?

805
00:38:38,380 --> 00:38:39,800
 Zato što već on

806
00:38:39,800 --> 00:38:40,640
 sa pet godine

807
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:42,440
 ima strah da će nešto propustiti,

808
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:43,720
 da neće dobiti priliku

809
00:38:43,720 --> 00:38:45,080
 za još jednom igračkom

810
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:46,740
 ako sad krivu izabere.

811
00:38:46,740 --> 00:38:47,840
 Da je zamisliti,

812
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:48,960
 to je djeto od pet godina.

813
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:49,960
 Ima taj strah.

814
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,120
 Mi odrasli isto imamo

815
00:38:51,120 --> 00:38:51,740
 te strahove.

816
00:38:51,740 --> 00:38:53,140
 Šta ako sam krivo izabrao

817
00:38:53,140 --> 00:38:53,780
 i više neće

818
00:38:53,780 --> 00:38:54,660
 kad neću imat priliku

819
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:55,360
 za nešto novo?

820
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:59,580
 I Bog mi neće dat blagoslovi.

821
00:38:59,580 --> 00:39:00,820
 Sad sam propustio blagoslov.

822
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:03,340
 Strah da ću propustiti nešto.

823
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:09,180
 Šta ako to odlučimo

824
00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:10,080
 da sam nešto propustiti,

825
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:11,200
 šta će se onda dogoditi?

826
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:12,060
 Ništa.

827
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,920
 Na kraju kraja cilje doći do neba.

828
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,660
 Doći ćemo nekako,

829
00:39:17,660 --> 00:39:18,680
 doguraćemo se.

830
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:22,600
 Ali ako ćeš razmišljati

831
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:23,700
 da si nešto propustili

832
00:39:23,700 --> 00:39:24,820
 da je moglo biti bolje,

833
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:26,600
 onda se nikad nećeš maknuti s mjesta.

834
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:31,140
 Druga stvar koja nam je prepreka

835
00:39:31,140 --> 00:39:33,000
 je kultura istripljenosti

836
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,500
 gdje toliko stvari moramo raditi

837
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:36,720
 i samo se napucamo,

838
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:37,740
 ja prvi,

839
00:39:37,740 --> 00:39:39,920
 raznim stvarima

840
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,940
 samo da smo zaokupljeni nečime

841
00:39:41,940 --> 00:39:43,520
 i onda nemamo trenutak

842
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:44,320
 gdje stvarno imamo

843
00:39:44,320 --> 00:39:45,780
 tišinu

844
00:39:45,780 --> 00:39:47,120
 i suzrati.

845
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:47,860
 Trenemo se s njim.

846
00:39:47,860 --> 00:39:50,560
 A to je ono sve što trebamo.

847
00:39:50,560 --> 00:39:52,000
 Trebamo trenutak

848
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:53,300
 da ga doživimo,

849
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,260
 da ga čujemo,

850
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:55,180
 da

851
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:57,820
 da možemo

852
00:39:57,820 --> 00:39:59,400
 reći

853
00:39:59,400 --> 00:40:00,540
 okej, imao sam trenutak

854
00:40:00,540 --> 00:40:01,560
 njegove prisutnosti.

855
00:40:01,560 --> 00:40:03,680
 Ako ne mogu

856
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:06,560
 se suočiti s tim,

857
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,680
 imam strah od...

858
00:40:08,680 --> 00:40:10,460
 Napisao sam prošli put

859
00:40:10,460 --> 00:40:11,020
 kad smo imali

860
00:40:11,020 --> 00:40:12,100
 night fear,

861
00:40:12,100 --> 00:40:13,080
 pa nisam mogu govoriti,

862
00:40:13,160 --> 00:40:13,820
 pa sam tu sjedio,

863
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:14,680
 pa sam bio frustriran,

864
00:40:14,680 --> 00:40:15,660
 pa sam se dizao iza,

865
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:16,660
 pa sam šetao iza,

866
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:17,480
 pa sam malo otišao van,

867
00:40:17,480 --> 00:40:18,800
 pa sam se vratio nazad unutra.

868
00:40:18,800 --> 00:40:19,700
 Zašto?

869
00:40:19,700 --> 00:40:21,220
 Ide super slavljenje,

870
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:21,680
 pjesma,

871
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:22,200
 pjevao bi,

872
00:40:22,200 --> 00:40:22,840
 ne mogu pjevat,

873
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:23,940
 ne mogu ništa izgovoriti,

874
00:40:24,020 --> 00:40:25,580
 samo mogu sjediti i šutiti.

875
00:40:25,580 --> 00:40:30,900
 A molitva je više biti nego činiti.

876
00:40:30,900 --> 00:40:34,480
 I zapravo nam Bog pocijetio da,

877
00:40:34,480 --> 00:40:35,780
 Marko,

878
00:40:35,780 --> 00:40:38,980
 nekad samo trebaš biti,

879
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:40,740
 a ne samo raditi.

880
00:40:40,740 --> 00:40:44,360
 Treća stvar koja nam je problema,

881
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:45,400
 to je zajedništvo.

882
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:48,400
 To je razumijevanje da

883
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:50,660
 odluke donosimo nekad skupa,

884
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:52,700
 da neke odluke trebamo prosuditi s drugima,

885
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:54,920
 da nismo sami sebi kriterij.

886
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:58,580
 Nego da ako imamo neki pocijeti,

887
00:40:58,580 --> 00:40:59,220
 nešto želimo,

888
00:40:59,220 --> 00:41:00,540
 pa okej, donesi to negdje.

889
00:41:00,540 --> 00:41:01,820
 Prosudi s drugima,

890
00:41:01,820 --> 00:41:02,860
 pa okej, šta ti misliš,

891
00:41:02,860 --> 00:41:04,020
 pa šta, kako ti vidiš.

892
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:06,400
 I da imamo to poznavanje,

893
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:08,020
 ne to površno poznavanje,

894
00:41:08,020 --> 00:41:09,920
 jedni od drugima,

895
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:11,760
 nego dublje.

896
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:14,140
 I onda i kad imamo neko dublje poznavanje,

897
00:41:14,140 --> 00:41:15,620
 onda ti taj netko može reći,

898
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:16,040
 pa znaš šta,

899
00:41:16,040 --> 00:41:17,200
 s obzirom na ovo tu,

900
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:19,100
 mislim da ti nije to pametna odluka.

901
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:26,620
 Trebamo biti otvoreni,

902
00:41:26,620 --> 00:41:29,200
 da trebamo druge.

903
00:41:29,200 --> 00:41:31,320
 Zajedništvo nam je potrebno.

904
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:33,900
 Da možemo zastati,

905
00:41:33,900 --> 00:41:35,320
 da mogu reći,

906
00:41:35,320 --> 00:41:37,920
 ne, nisam ja jedini najpometniji,

907
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:39,900
 ne, ne znam ja najbolje,

908
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:41,840
 i da je transavijet drugih.

909
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:47,680
 Koliko god mi se ne sviđa,

910
00:41:47,680 --> 00:41:51,440
 i koliko god mi zna srezati ideju odmah,

911
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,700
 moja žena,

912
00:41:52,700 --> 00:41:56,420
