913
00:41:56,420 --> 00:42:01,100
 I koliko god se bunim,

914
00:42:01,100 --> 00:42:02,040
 i ljutim,

915
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,940
 i mislim si, možda nije trebalo,

916
00:42:03,940 --> 00:42:05,080
 tako, nije baš svaki put,

917
00:42:05,080 --> 00:42:05,880
